* Iron Raptor clenched her jaw as she heaved herself to her feet, trying to 
ignore the intense pain in her side.
< I'll deal with that later, I have work to do now.>
Snarling she hefted her sword from the ground and straightened herself up, 
taking in a beep breath and holding it as she moved out into the thinning 
ash.
There were Alliance bots in the battle now and she was almost ready to yell 
in frustration when she somehow heard through the ash that they were 
fighting on the Maximal side?
Every step seered into her mind but she'de felt worse before, this was 
nothing that she couldn't take.
Her scanners detected a target, not too far from her location and was big 
enough that it might take a good beating.
Motormaster.
Quickly sliding her sword back into place her shoulder-plates retracted and 
swung around, a pair of guns locking into place around wasit hight (like TM 
Optimus's.) She targeted carefully and fired towards him, keeping her 
fingers on the triggers and sending a total of 16 high voltage charges 
towards him.*
